      <title>HPS 向贝莱德出售后提供激励措施以留住员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hps-offers-incentives-to-retain-staff-after-sale-to-blackrock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻看到的一封投资者信显示，HPS Investment Partners 正在向员工提供五年内归属的激励措施，以鼓励他们在被贝莱德收购后继续留任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hps-offers-incentives-to-retain-staff-after-sale-to-blackrock</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国关闭俄罗斯加密货币富豪网络，转移寡头数十亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方表示，他们已经关闭了俄罗斯网络，该网络通过在欧洲、中东和南美洲交换现金和加密货币，为寡头、街头帮派和间谍转移数十亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰瑟枪和马斯克激励的薪酬方案让 Axon 首席执行官成为亿万富翁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/tasers-and-musk-inspired-pay-package-make-axon-ceo-a-billionaire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Axon Enterprise Inc. 的 CEO 薪酬方案模仿了埃隆·马斯克在特斯拉公司的激励措施，采取了高风险、高回报的策略。现在马斯克和 Axon 联合创始人里克·史密斯还有另一个共同点：他们都是亿万富翁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/tasers-and-musk-inspired-pay-package-make-axon-ceo-a-billionaire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国股市刚刚打破三年连跌纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-12-04/investors-add-uk-equities-ending-three-year-loss-for-london-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不要太兴奋，但上个月，英国股票基金自 2021 年初以来首次出现净流入。]]></description>
