    <item>
      <title>前瑞士银行家旗下 47 亿美元财富公司瞄准迈阿密财富</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ex-swiss-banker-s-4-7-billion-wealth-firm-targets-miami-riches</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自五年前在摩纳哥创立财富公司 Azura 以来，阿里·贾马尔迅速将其服务扩展到全球富人，在新加坡、日内瓦和纽约等地设立了办事处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ex-swiss-banker-s-4-7-billion-wealth-firm-targets-miami-riches</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多伦多房屋销售量攀升，买家纷纷重返市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/toronto-housing-sales-climb-with-buyers-flocking-back-to-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利率下降吸引买家重返市场，多伦多房屋销售连续第四个月增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/toronto-housing-sales-climb-with-buyers-flocking-back-to-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪拜亿万富翁计划在亚洲各地建立数据中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/dubai-billionaire-plans-to-build-data-centers-across-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达马克集团 (Damac Group) 由亿万富翁开发商侯赛因·萨基瓦尼 (Hussain Sajwani) 支持，计划投资约 30 亿美元在东南亚地区建设数据中心，因为该地区将成为人工智能和云服务的枢纽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/dubai-billionaire-plans-to-build-data-centers-across-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 06:42:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉里·芬克正在让新一代亿万富翁比他更富有</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/fink-mints-more-fortunes-bigger-than-his-in-private-markets-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着拉里·芬克推动贝莱德公司进一步进军私人市场，他不断为这家资产管理巨头的名单增添新的亿万富翁——并在此过程中让他们都比他更富有。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/fink-mints-more-fortunes-bigger-than-his-in-private-markets-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 17:40:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁萨利纳斯的 Elektra 股价跌至 2007 年以来的最低水平，因跌势进一步加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/salinas-elektra-sinks-to-lowest-since-2007-as-rout-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，Grupo Elektra 股价跌至 2007 年以来的最低水平，随后有所反弹，两天的交易中，控股股东里卡多·萨利纳斯·普利戈 (Ricardo Salinas Pliego) 的财富蒸发逾 50 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/salinas-elektra-sinks-to-lowest-since-2007-as-rout-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 16:47:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克数十亿美元的特斯拉赔偿被法官裁定无效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/musk-record-tesla-pay-package-rejected-again-by-delaware-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克创纪录的特斯拉公司薪酬方案再次被特拉华州法官推翻，这可能会让这位世界首富、唐纳德·特朗普最亲密的亲信损失数十亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/musk-record-tesla-pay-package-rejected-again-by-delaware-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 21:49:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
